# Cross-platform line endings. Force LF in the repo and the working tree so
# generated code (build_runner *.g.dart / *.freezed.dart) stops flipping between
# CRLF and LF on Windows checkouts (core.autocrlf=true was causing spurious
# "modified" entries after every `gate.sh` run).
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicit binary assets — never normalize.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.webp binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.bmp binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.mp3 binary
*.m4a binary
*.wav binary
*.ogg binary
*.keystore binary
*.jks binary
*.aar binary
*.jar binary
*.so binary
